Then I'm gonna do what
everybody else with a job does.

13:36.642 --> 13:38.743
I'm gonna suck it up.
I'm gonna do the work.

13:38.744 --> 13:39.977
All right.

13:39.979 --> 13:42.080
But know that if you do
decide to quit,

13:42.081 --> 13:44.649
all my fancy new duds
can go back to Mervyns.

13:44.650 --> 13:46.216
Except the hat.

13:46.218 --> 13:48.185
Aw, you love your hat.

13:48.187 --> 13:49.587
I do. But more importantly,

13:49.588 --> 13:51.990
you know that weird sweat ring
I leave on my pillowcase?

13:51.991 --> 13:54.057
The same thing happened
in the fedora.

14:00.431 --> 14:02.567
All right, all right.

14:02.568 --> 14:03.735
Here we go.

14:03.736 --> 14:05.369
We got this.

14:05.370 --> 14:07.705
Mm-hmm.

14:07.706 --> 14:09.173
Got that. Okay.

14:09.174 --> 14:12.742
Just plug my nose
and dive right in.

14:13.644 --> 14:20.584
She closed her eyes in
ecstasy and awoke in...

14:20.586 --> 14:22.386
Uh, the rope went down...

14:22.387 --> 14:26.056
Oh... 1776!

14:26.058 --> 14:28.359
Okay, 1776 it is!

14:28.360 --> 14:34.532
1776... In the distance,
she heard the town crier.

14:34.533 --> 14:36.417
Hear ye.

14:37.835 --> 14:40.136
Hear ye!

14:43.808 --> 14:44.942
Mr. Franklin!

14:44.943 --> 14:47.877
Mr. Benjamin Franklin!

14:47.879 --> 14:49.445
At your service.
Please.

14:49.447 --> 14:50.748
Don't be frightened.

14:50.749 --> 14:51.949
And I know this may sound odd,

14:51.950 --> 14:54.385
but I need to tell you
that I'm from...

14:54.386 --> 14:56.219
from the future.

14:56.221 --> 14:59.156
Now, I'm sure that this
scares you to your core,

14:59.157 --> 15:01.625
