that I'm not here to harm you.

15:01.626 --> 15:04.395
In fact, I'm here
to make love to you.

15:04.396 --> 15:07.364
And when we do it,
we need to do it well.

15:07.365 --> 15:09.033
So well, in fact,
that our lovemaking

15:09.034 --> 15:11.035
will send me forward
into the future.

15:11.036 --> 15:16.072
Exactly 238 years into the
arms of my one true love.

15:17.207 --> 15:19.609
All right, let's get rutting.

15:19.611 --> 15:21.845
Wait, wait. You're one
of history's greatest scholars,

15:21.846 --> 15:24.381
a scientist and a statesman.

15:24.382 --> 15:25.982
You're just gonna buy into this?

15:25.984 --> 15:27.284
Hey, don't look at me, lady.

15:27.285 --> 15:29.719
You're the one writing
this horse crap.

15:29.721 --> 15:32.588
Just shut up
and take off your pants.

15:33.757 --> 15:35.391
(groans)

15:39.329 --> 15:41.964
Molly?

15:41.966 --> 15:45.401
Use your fingers.

15:55.966 --> 15:58.502
So, how's our
sexy sci-fi coming?

15:58.503 --> 16:01.971
Oh, chug, chug, chugging along.

16:01.973 --> 16:03.707
(chuckles) Well, good.

16:03.708 --> 16:06.143
Just know this... your whole
world is about to change.

16:06.144 --> 16:08.178
You won't be able to
walk down the street

16:08.179 --> 16:09.613
without someone
pointing and saying,

16:09.614 --> 16:11.248
"There's the <i>Timegasm</i> lady""

16:11.249 --> 16:12.716
Ah!

16:12.717 --> 16:15.952
And that's the thought
that keeps me up at night.

16:15.953 --> 16:20.190
Oh... but, you know, but I...
I am having a bit of a dilemma.

16:20.191 --> 16:23.860
And you're the smartest person
that I know,

16:23.861 --> 16:26.396
so I've...
I've come to you for help.

16:26.397 --> 16:28.198
Ah, they all do.

16:28.199 --> 16:29.533
Oh.

16:29.534 --> 16:30.766
It's in the writing.

16:30.768 --> 16:32.535
Mm-hmm.
I've... I've come across

16:32.536 --> 16:35.205
this character...
brilliant man, handsome.

16:35.206 --> 16:36.873
I mean, almost beautiful.

16:36.874 --> 16:39.509
Uh, born in England,
studied at Oxford.

16:39.510 --> 16:41.578
As did I.

16:41.579 --> 16:42.911
No, you didn't.

16:42.913 --> 16:44.581
Yes.
No, you didn't!

16:44.582 --> 16:45.647
Yes.
Oh, my!

16:45.649 --> 16:46.816
That's... Gah!

16:46.817 --> 16:48.852
That's crazy. I, uh...

16:48.853 --> 16:50.186
You know what?
It's funny.

16:50.187 --> 16:51.688
'Cause now that you say that,

16:51.689 --> 16:53.723
