and thinking about him,

16:53.724 --> 16:55.859
I'm... You are very similar.

16:55.860 --> 16:57.093
You're very well put together.

16:57.094 --> 16:58.995
Very self-assured.

16:58.996 --> 17:00.697
Is he tall?

17:00.698 --> 17:01.931
Oh! Yeah, I mean, yeah,

17:01.932 --> 17:04.199
